item.title: 2019-04-18: Honeymoon Day3
item.description: English Breakfast I ate English breakfast in England for the first time. It was lovely delicious. Afternoon tea At last I had an afternoon tea in England. The tea is lovely tasty, and scones with plenty of clotted cream too. I enjoyed the afternoon tea. Timeline
